data.description: Completely updated home on large corner lot. Large living/dining with hardwood floors. Kitchen has new flooring, granite counter tops, large walk in Pantry, dining, Refrigerator, Range/Oven, Dishwasher and great cabinet space.  Hall Bathroom is completely updated with tiled Shower/Tub, new pedestal sink and toilet. Master has large walk-in closet, completely new bath with tiled walk in Shower and a unique vanity and sink. This home has a large utility, new garage, wood deck and fence plus a 16 x 12 storage unit. New Central H/A, all new windows, and metal roof.  Beautiful corner lot. Square footage includes garage
